The paper focuses on image classification with deep learning, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses methods for training deep neural networks with label noise, which falls under the subfields of machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE, cs.DL).
